content.rendered:
Directed by Vikram K. Kumar

Written by B.V.S. Ravi. Vikram K. Kumar. B.V.S. Ravi. Mukund Pandey

Star Raashi Khanna(Priya). Prakash Raj(Rao). Naga Chaitanya Akkineni(Abhiram). Avika Gor(Sravani). Malavika Nair(Paaru). Sampath Raj(Narayana Rao). Easwari Rao(Sailaja). Srinivas Avasarala(Karthik). Tulasi(Abhi’s mother). Sai Sushanth Reddy(Sharwa). Bharath Reddy(Coach). R.J. Hemant(Office Employee). Aayush Agarwal(Satish).Chakravarthii

Language Telugu

Producers Ivano Fucci. Dil Raju. Harshith Reddy. Sireesh. Dmitriy D. Zaytsev

Production Sri Venkateswara Creations
